Veteran Nigerian singer, Sound Sultan has celebrated his 10th wedding anniversary with his wife, Farida. Sound Sultan and his wife Farida Fasasi are celebrating their 10th wedding anniversary today, October 1. The veteran Nigerian singer took to Instagram to share the lovely photo below of himself and his beautiful wife posing together and then penned her a sweet note. He wrote: ’10 years of PURE HAPPINESS AND REAL LOVE .with you @faridafasasi it has always been organic happiness.”Thank you for being yourself and for being my backbone .keeping me looking young and vibrant . Make sure your marriage sweet pass your wedding ..”Happy wedding Anniversary #10yearsaboo” Source